I looked over your, uh,
Cubs/Marlins tape.

34:38.275 --> 34:39.266
-- Yes?
-- And it's good.

34:39.344 --> 34:40.641
-- Thank you.
-- It's very good.

34:40.712 --> 34:42.908
-- Especially for your first time out.
-- Thank you very much.

