their appreciation of baseball.

38:26.437 --> 38:28.235
God knows
you've affected mine.

38:28.306 --> 38:30.104
Casey,
what are you working on?

38:30.174 --> 38:31.232
An epic miniseries.

38:31.309 --> 38:32.242
It's the Cubs/Marlins.

38:32.343 --> 38:33.902
