39:09.914 --> 39:11.040
You got a whisk?

39:11.115 --> 39:13.243
A whisk?

39:13.317 --> 39:14.307
Yes.

39:14.385 --> 39:15.546
That's the thing you --

39:15.620 --> 39:16.951
For scrambled eggs.

39:17.021 --> 39:20.753
You -- You stir it
really fast in a bowl.

39:20.825 --> 39:23.453
-- I can't just use the fork?
